reviews.review_text:
Set List - Rate 1 to 10 One helluva set for their home venue..what era do you think the bad was at its tightest? I think 1987- 1990 , maybe 91 - 92 ish... then things went into a little decline..
But this show i especially would of loved to have been there.. God Bless The Grateful Dead🎸💀😎
